GoPhish
Open-source phishing framework

Social Engineering
Description
GoPhish is a powerful, open-source phishing framework that makes it easy to test your organization's exposure to phishing.

Installation / Check
Check if installed:

which gophish
Install command:

wget https://github.com/gophish/gophish/releases/download/v0.12.1/gophish-v0.12.1-linux-64bit.zip
Basic Syntax
./gophish
Common Commands
Command	What it does	When to use	Risk
./gophish

Start GoPhish server	Launch phishing platform	
Access https://localhost:3333

Admin interface	Configure campaigns	
Step-by-Step Guide
1
Start GoPhish server
2
Access admin panel
3
Create email template
4
Create landing page
5
Setup sending profile
6
Create user group
7
Launch campaign
Understanding the Output
Web dashboard showing campaign statistics, clicks, and submissions.

